## Example 4: Resilience Engine — AI-Powered Major Incident Management
**URL**: https://cutover.com/blog/resilience-engine-ai-powered-major-incident-management-enterprise-it
**Topic**: How AI changes the major incident management playbook for enterprise IT
**Audience**: Head of Infrastructure & Ops, CISO, Major Incident Managers

### What to replicate
- Frame AI not as a replacement for human judgment but as a **force multiplier**
- Use the "co-pilot" framing: AI handles the grunt work (log triage, status updates, comms), humans handle the strategy
- Contrast the old way (manual, chaotic, reactive) with the new way (structured, orchestrated, AI-assisted)
- Tie back to a concrete metric: MTTR reduction is the north star

